notes: intransitive; often used with 'da'; past participle 'distato'
example_sentence_italian: Distare è un verbo poco usato.
example_sentence_english: To be distant is a little-used verb.

example_sentence_italian: Distando solo due chilometri, si può andare a piedi.
example_sentence_english: Being only two kilometers away, you can walk.

example_sentence_italian: Il paese è distato cento chilometri dalla città.
example_sentence_english: The town has been one hundred kilometers from the city.

example_sentence_italian: La frazione è distata cento chilometri dalla città.
example_sentence_english: The hamlet has been one hundred kilometers from the city.

example_sentence_italian: I paesi sono distati diversi chilometri.
example_sentence_english: The towns have been several kilometers away.

example_sentence_italian: Le isole sono distate a largo.
example_sentence_english: The islands have been far offshore.

example_sentence_italian: Io disto poco dalla città.
example_sentence_english: I am a short distance from the city.

example_sentence_italian: Tu disti molto da me.
example_sentence_english: You are far from me.

translation_english: he is distant/she is distant/you (formal) are distant
example_sentence_italian: Il villaggio dista dieci chilometri.
example_sentence_english: The village is ten kilometers away.

example_sentence_italian: Voi distate poco dal museo.
example_sentence_english: You are a short distance from the museum.

example_sentence_italian: Le case distano poche centinaia di metri dalla stazione.
example_sentence_english: The houses are a few hundred meters from the station.

example_sentence_italian: Quand'ero piccolo, io distavo poco dalla città.
example_sentence_english: When I was small, I was a short distance from the city.

example_sentence_italian: Da ragazzo, tu distavi molto dai compagni.
example_sentence_english: As a boy, you were far from your classmates.

translation_english: he was distant/she was distant/you (formal) were distant
example_sentence_italian: All'epoca la scuola distava poco dal paese.
example_sentence_english: At the time the school was not far from the town.

example_sentence_italian: Noi distavamo pochi metri dalla piazza.
example_sentence_english: We were a few meters from the square.

example_sentence_italian: Quando vivevate lì, voi distavate molto dalla città.
example_sentence_english: When you lived there, you were far from the city.

example_sentence_italian: Allora loro distavano pochi chilometri dalla costa.
example_sentence_english: Back then, they were a few kilometers from the coast.
